data.clean_description: 999 Pure German. BASF. Grade GBL solution. Instructions for use DILUTE your dose in a big volume of liquid before drinking , NEVER drink straight. GBL in it s pure form is very irritant and could burn your mouth and throat. Dose range 1 - 15 ml , do not exceed 2 ml. Re-dosing. Carefully with 1 ml leaving at least 1 hour intervals. DO NOT mix with alcohol or other depressants , this greatly increases the potency. GBL can be very dangerous if not taken carefully and with respect , please inform yourself and use it responsibly.
data.name: 500ml Pure GBL
